6. EDITOR

You can load your saved data into the editor and change your team name,
stadium and the names of the stands.

Once you load the editor you have to load your saved data. The data will
be displayed on the screen.

Click on the icon to the left of the data you want to edit, then type in the
new information.

When you are happy with the changes, save the data then reload Euro Manager.

