7. HISTORY

British Football - October 1995.
Released through F1 Licenceware as part of the Strategy Games Pack in
January 1996.
Had only ten teams, one league, no cups and no tactics.

British Manager  - July 1996.
Released through 5th Dimension Licenceware.
Slight improvement with forty teams, four leagues, two cups and editor.
Reviews in Amiga Action (December 1996) and CU Amiga (August 1997).

